18  Neikilikuan oltung'ani obo oitoreisho ajoki, “Laai teng'enani supat, kaji aiko pee ajung enkishui oo ntarasi?” 
19  Nejoki Yesu ninye, “Ainyoo pee kijo kara supat? Meetae hoo obo supat leme Enkai ake. 
20   Iyiolo iyie nkitanapat.

‘Miloloito,

miar likae metua,

mipurrisho,

minteeniki likae elejare

iyanyita minyi o ng'utunyi.’ ”


21  Nejoki ninye, “Aibung'a kuna pooki ebaiki apa ara oti.”


22  Ore pee ening Yesu ina, nejoki, “Kitong'orikia nabo toki. Timira pooki toki niaata tooriki laisinak, naa itum olchumati te shumata; wou taa tusujuaki.” 
23  Kake ina ake etoning'o neisinanuo oleng, amu karsis apa naleng. 
24  Neing'or Yesu ninye nejo, “Egol taa duoo to ltung'ani oata imasaa pee ejing enkitoria e Nkai! 
25  Amu elelek te ntames pee eim enaudoto o ltidu alang oltung'ani karsis te nejing enkitoria e Nkai.” 
26  Nejo lelo ootoning'o, “Ai ng'ae naa doi eitajeuni?” 
27  Kake etejo, “Ore enemeidimayu too ltung'ana keidimayu te Nkai.” 
28  Nejo Petero, “Ng'ura, kitung'uaitie iyiook inkang'itie ang nikisuj iyie.” 
29  Nejoki Yesu ninche, “Edede, ajoki intae, meetae oltung'ani otung'uayie enkaji, aashu enkitok aashu, lalashera, aashu ntoiwuo aashu nkera, te nkaraki enkitoria e Nkai, 
30  lemetum nkatitin kumok taata te na kata, ore te idia kata nalotu netum enkishui oo ntarasi.”

